text: Guess What may refer to: * Guess What (Canadian game show), a 1983–1987 Canadian game show that aired on CTV * Guess What (U.S. game show), a 1952 American game show that aired on DuMont network * "Guess What" (song), a song by Syleena Johnson * Guess What? a 1990 picture book for children
title: Guess What
